{"type": "article", "id": 21156, "title": "卧室装修难以出彩？来看看这两个脑洞很大的案例", "description": "一个把床藏起来，一个给卧室安装了滑梯。", "date": "2016-01-22T17:26:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 22564, "name": "卧室"}, {"id": 12527, "name": "收纳"}, {"id": 1871, "name": "装修"}, {"id": 22567, "name": "滑梯"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 18, "praise_count": 624, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703180638BTpdnQrvO50S26bz.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t装修的时候，不少人喜欢在客厅、飘窗、洗手间里下功夫，而卧室却大多千篇一律。这里有两个大胆的卧室装修案例：\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607031806299OJ243hqjBIk1yER.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"420\" title=\"猜猜这个白盒子是做什么的？\" alt=\"猜猜这个白盒子是做什么的？\" data-ratio=\"0.525\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>猜猜这个白盒子是做什么的？</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180630v57wDYxHJUdiF9lR.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"628\" title=\"里面是一张床！\" alt=\"里面是一张床！\" data-ratio=\"0.785\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>从另一个角度望去，里面是一张床！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180630w0E3F2JeUG4q6t9j.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"913\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"1.14125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">全景图\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180631K9plsyeVuMkFBRZv.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"365\" title=\"概念图\" alt=\"概念图\" data-ratio=\"0.45625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>概念图</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t上图中的这个卧室是 <a href=\"http://ecdm.eu/\">ECDM</a> 设计事务所设计的，主导设计师是 Emmanuel\r\nCombarel 和 Dominique Marrec，<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2016/01/21/youll-never-guess-whats-inside-the-hanging-cube-in-this-apartment/\" target=\"_blank\">这是一个巴基斯坦设计事务所</a>。白色立方体是金属结构的，覆盖有木板，木板外是白色的聚氨酯树脂涂层，白色立方体节省了空间。下面则是另外一个案例：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180631QINeFt4g2sDBEju8.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" title=\"滑梯从二楼延伸下来\" alt=\"滑梯从二楼延伸下来\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>设计师设计了一个滑梯，从二楼延伸下来</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180632jCJ7IvLyKnHTDc8q.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"1063\" title=\"另一个角度\" alt=\"另一个角度\" data-ratio=\"1.32875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>另一个角度</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607031806332IzBdCKb1G5S74jl.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180633ZajfMVCUoeXtsbHG.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"624\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.78\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180634y5tiYEDUavrkxWoZ.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">滑梯直接连通到卧室\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180635ts8SjbRnCwYLJkMd.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607031806359RLkgsKDqlzej2wM.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180636e8nUNz2cpb5lZKoP.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"1036\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"1.295\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180636bONGywotQmWJeXMD.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180637OqxX1FHRkSsrwz3L.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"578\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.7225\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180637SlygcEjarbUtehGP.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"1199\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"1.49875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t上图这个案例源于乌克兰设计事务所<a href=\"http://www.kidesign.com.ua\" target=\"_blank\"> Ki Design Studio</a>。<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2016/01/20/this-apartment-interior-was-designed-with-a-slide-into-the-living-room/\" target=\"_blank\">它最大的亮点就是从二楼延伸至一层卧室的滑梯。</a>以前房屋的二层是闲置的，屋主邀请设计师对房间进行改造，要求是“打败无趣”，设计师们便设计了一个连通楼上楼下的滑梯，楼梯的尽头是滑梯的入口，一个旧房子，化身为居家场所、孩子的游乐场、家庭的办公室。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2016/01/21/youll-never-guess-whats-inside-the-hanging-cube-in-this-apartment/\" target=\"_blank\">contemporist</a> \r\n</p>\n\n"}